{"tid":2382814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紅磡指定區域內有多間長生店 業界憂如突襲封區礙先人出殯","createTime":"2021-01-27T13:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T00:05:37.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d95b453c145a04926a8f94f4df4a3086a9efe30","tid":2382814,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"紅磡指定區域內有大量長生店、花鋪及石廠。殯儀業商會理事長郭凱邦接受電台訪問時指，有業內人士擔心會進一步封區，已經提前將物資盡量遷走。他又認為即使只封一晚都會影響整個出殯程序，政府要承擔責任，並希望可以預早至少兩至三天通知業界，或表明只針對「三無大廈」住戶，不影響殯儀業運作。<br />\n<br />\n指定區域內的長生店職員陳先生，從事殯儀業近10年。他說農曆年前這段時間最忙，靈車可能一日要跑幾趟，往來棺材舖、醫院和火葬場，一日不下於一單出殯。他認為如果政府突然封鎖指定區域的幾條街，最直接的影響就是出不了殯。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生說：「你今日唔做今日嗰啲（出殯），聽日、後日都已經排哂期，咁要褪幾耐呢？ 褪嘅期間副嘢擺邊度呢？ 所以其實無得褪，流程係好死的，定咗嗰日係冇更改嘅餘地。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到會如何應對，他表示：「行內冇咩準備，咪就係將最重要嘅文件、要用嘅文件跟身，其他到時再隨機應變，但你剩係諗吓都已經好恐怖。」以他所知，殯儀業商會正與政府周旋，「但係你唔知個政府諗啲咩，佢鍾意封就到時先算，咁都無辦法。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/37584/%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1-%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%8D%80%E5%9F%9F-%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-37584/%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%8D%80%E5%9F%9F%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E9%95%B7%E7%94%9F%E5%BA%97-%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%86%82%E5%A6%82%E7%AA%81%E8%A5%B2%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E7%A4%99%E5%85%88%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E6%AE%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F37584%2F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25A3%25A1-%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%259F%259F-%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-37584%2F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25A3%25A1%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%259F%259F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%2586%2582%25E5%25A6%2582%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%2585%2588%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25AE%25AF&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdnzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=3fe95ea1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/37584/%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1-%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%8D%80%E5%9F%9F-%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-37584/%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%8D%80%E5%9F%9F%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E9%95%B7%E7%94%9F%E5%BA%97-%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%86%82%E5%A6%82%E7%AA%81%E8%A5%B2%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E7%A4%99%E5%85%88%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E6%AE%AF</a>"},{"pid":"91d79164520a296bce164e48ef6a7335c23c970f","tid":2382814,"uid":180401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T14:05:53.000Z","msg":"封封封 長生店係咩組織控制？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a640dccfa1d7ca02b3a8cfdd02afe5cdedd62dfb","tid":2382814,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T14:08:01.000Z","msg":"醃鹹魚"},{"pid":"e02742b1616fd3b92527eae4ee593142b0166b51","tid":2382814,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"阻住樓主全家出殯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要反"},{"pid":"b90f657505537b639e143c0036e2206319dca5d5","tid":2382814,"uid":135169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"黎生（鹹魚）：我嘅訴求就係出殯"},{"pid":"d59f7ac95b102604b9bdc12eadefbd8649246de9","tid":2382814,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T00:01:40.000Z","msg":"係街搭個爐燒囉。"},{"pid":"ea20d4d3384f0e83820f168ab595b1391e1a5c7f","tid":2382814,"uid":340192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T00:05:37.000Z","msg":"班長生店咪又係黑社會<br />\n自己友唔怕啦"}]}